<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[الإِرْهَابُ]</span>: الإِخافة،<span class="c5"> قال الله تعالى:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>تُرْهِبُونَ بِهِ عَدُوَّ اللّاهِ وَعَدُوَّكُمْ <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
